cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper is about Particle Swarm Optimization (PSO), which is a nature-inspired meta-heuristic for solving continuous optimization problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper deals with the analysis of the behavior of particles in the swarm, which is related to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the convergence of PSO, which is related to Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
